HX-2024-07-03:
(*
Wed 03 Jul 2024 09:21:50 AM EDT
*)
//
ATS3/Xanadu/srcgen1:
This project was the first attempt to implement ATS3!
It started around April, 2018 and produced a typechecker
(xatsopt) and then a compiler (xats2js) by November, 2020.
//
Note that ATS3/Xanadu/srcgen1 is written in ATS2 and the
compiler for the project is ATS2/Postiats.
//
